{"tid":2058244,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動］0615 黑衫白絲帶行動，太古廣場見","createTime":"2020-06-10T04:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T05:48:02.000Z","uid":38610,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0ceec3b9a58cf29d73791987a061250bebd058","tid":2058244,"uid":38610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T04:21:12.000Z","msg":"反修例示威爆發一周年，民間人權陣線呼籲全港市民，在 6 月 15 日、梁凌杰死忌當天，穿黑衣並繫上白絲帶悼念，民陣召集人岑子杰表示，民陣秘書處到時會到太古廣場外獻花，「他是第一條命，我們不能忘記。」他又表示和警方商討時，警方曾要求民陣「可否不要公開講悼念」，但民陣已拒絕，他亦已致函政務司司長張建宗，要求他運用權力批准民陣的集會要求，「他光明正大地為香港人犠牲，為何我們去紀念他、表達敬意時，我們要私底下靜悄悄，好似唔見得光咁去做？我不認同。」<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/民陣籲-615-全民黑衣悼梁凌杰-警要求私下悼念-民陣拒絕-當天八人太官廣場獻花/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E7%B1%B2-615-%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E6%82%BC%E6%A2%81%E5%87%8C%E6%9D%B0-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%A7%81%E4%B8%8B%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95-%E7%95%B6%E5%A4%A9%E5%85%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%AA%E5%AE%98%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E7%8D%BB%E8%8A%B1%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVay9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=1ec405e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E7%B1%B2-615-%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E6%82%BC%E6%A2%81%E5%87%8C%E6%9D%B0-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%A7%81%E4%B8%8B%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95-%E7%95%B6%E5%A4%A9%E5%85%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%AA%E5%AE%98%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E7%8D%BB%E8%8A%B1%2F&h=35c9911e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/民陣籲-615-全民黑衣悼梁凌杰-警要求私下悼念-民陣拒絕-當天八人太官廣場獻花/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGfpdWD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGfpdWD.png&h=a3aa9ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>梁烈士為香港民族種下種子，他日終會發揚光大<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑衫白絲帶為記<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">金鐘見<img src=